Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say this once, so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:17.93,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:23.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:30.02,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:35.99,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:43.37,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:48.08,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:54.01,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:02.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:07.81,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:14.94,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:21.70,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:17.93,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:23.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:30.02,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:35.99,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:43.37,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:48.08,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:54.01,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:02.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:07.81,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:14.94,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:21.70,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:41.76,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)\pos(140,384)}Episode 5 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was with boy I've liked since spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I had confessed to him once before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I didn't really understand the response I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I thought that it was all over for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if it were a miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I saw the entire world change before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano cast a spell on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get a wink of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, is your face puffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do about my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he was a really annoying, loud-mouth classmate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but because of what happened, I was up all night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wondering how to face him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing went pretty well the other day, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... it's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be able to look him straight in the face anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take a look at this. Looks cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.48,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You. Is it true that you and Yano kissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? When did...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you! Spill the beans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... we were seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's going on now? Are you two gonna go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you'd better not come to me with your love problems anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'll definitely support you when you're breaking up, so come to me for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be dating, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano hasn't said anything to me yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I haven't gotten any text messages...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he never sent me any text messages before, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's slowly starting to get on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... they said that thing will be on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay? You seem a little out of it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's because I couldn't get to sleep last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a moron for not being able to fall asleep over a kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what was he talking about? He's reminding me about upcoming events?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat after me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a student council meeting at three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thursday, a student council event review meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday, the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a student council meeting at three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tuesday--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thursday, the event review meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a student council meeting at three. Lunch at twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday, the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a student council meeting at three. Lunch at twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thursday, the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron. Saturday, the event. Today, a movie at four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... what's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, the student council meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thursday, the event review meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday, the event!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a movie at four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct! Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a m-movie at four?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A movie... at four?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart hasn't stopped pounding since this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet how can you say that stuff so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that cute smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I feel so relieved, my sleepiness has caught up with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano finally smiled at me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means it wasn't a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't taking it the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened yesterday really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, she's still sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she sleep at all last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana! The student council meeting's at three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A date... a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:51.57,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Sign: A date... a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's already this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the student council meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot... it's long over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lef--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the student council meeting in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took notes for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are the handouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take survey during homeroom, and this is to be submitted next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, a guy who finds everything a pain and skips out all the time, did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it to the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait one sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After watching the movie and getting something to drink, I wonder if we'll go out to eat, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't forget bus fare, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that. I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's an open seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think I'll stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna get more crowded, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm wearing myself out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to act natural... natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... h-hot chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there are a lot of open seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I should've asked for a milk tea....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... I'm pushing myself too hard again... I need to act natural! Natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you liked movies, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially because it's so dark, if you know what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I rest my arm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, you can also rest your arm here if you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seat next to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a lot closer than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie was about a woman who kept passing by the one she loved without realizing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! There they go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and let them meet each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were finally able to meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... kept half of the armrest free the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that having mutual feelings for each other is great.
