Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:09.14,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90\fscy96.25\frz358.215\pos(538,251)\c&H607074&}Cutesy girl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Taka-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We Were There Too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there! I'm Mizuguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Nagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving straight to our topic of the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Nanami kissing him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was really surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me want to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, when... when did Nanami fall for Yano, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down, Mizu-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never listen to her love problems ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't just leave Nanami alone, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.45,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the second half of the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That movie was really good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The ending was really moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What scenes did you like, Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...liked the part where we held hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because I got so whirled up today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano just seems different than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They way he speaks, and his behavior... The intonation in his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all different than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad if I made you go out of your way today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home after we finish eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a kind person, under everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until the other day, you were mean to me all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you suddenly become such different person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you told me you loved me, did you not love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, my girlfriend isn't the same as my other classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you're the one who's become different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This basically means that you're an insider in my circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An insider?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Everyone else is split into insiders and outsiders, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really want to hold Yano tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been with anyone special for this event before...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this year, it's different!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the problem here is that Yano has a better sense for this sort of stuff than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be careful so he doesn't say something like "laaame" to what I get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what sort of things make boys happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he doesn't have anything to say, Yano unexpectedly comes really close sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only when no one's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to answer seriously.
