Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.54,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\alpha&H20&\p1\c&H7E5749&\fscx117.5\fscy146.25\frz8.76\pos(535,207)}m -2 -10 b -2 -10 -2 -10 -2 -10 b 0 -13 3 -16 5 -20 b 4 -21 4 -21 3 -21 b 3 -21 2 -20 1 -19 b 1 -19 0 -18 0 -18 b 1 -24 2 -31 3 -37 b 1 -38 1 -38 2 -38 b 1 -37 0 -38 0 -35 b -1 -30 -2 -24 -3 -18 b -4 -19 -4 -19 -5 -21 b -7 -21 -7 -20 -7 -19 b -5 -15 -4 -13 -2 -10 b -2 -10 -2 -10 -2 -10{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worcester sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.59,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Soy sauce tastes best with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's definitely Worcester sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just when I thought they weren't getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worcester sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worcester sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you, it's all about the soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:37.55,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two arguing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, which is better on sunny-side up eggs, soy sauce or Worcester sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must seem like stupid love birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says, soy sauce will remain on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure shows off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's deja vu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I didn't think you could be such a doofus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're unexpectedly childish, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get some pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, how do you have so much money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents give me whatever I ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are really stingy, and they won't even give me allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bum money off them by doing the whole filial piety thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's hand is warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... whenever I touch it, my heart lets out a small squeal of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's your hand so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are more sensitive to the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, what do you want for your present?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, and this time, excluding living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano must've realized that I only have a small allowance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really watching out for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I want to give him something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as long as you're there, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It was just so embarrassing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... there's such bad taste in my mouth now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter came quickly this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.97,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx112.5\fscy105\pos(459,156)\frx28\fry18\frz348.773\c&H685B8F&}Girls Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my heart is warm and cozy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I kinda feel like I've become prettier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious? Talk about bad taste in girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so ugly, so why did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... young girls these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just jealous, so don't take it to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They were talking about me? "Ugly" and all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm now in a position where people are jealous of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are a lot of other girls who cried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want for your Christmas present?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano likes the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, am I ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugly girls are more... impressive with their looks, to put it a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, am I beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful girls are more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honest bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you find attractive about me, Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cute, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I sometimes get anxious like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Yano touches me with his warm hands, my heart clenches up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided on what I want for a Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me that you'll never leave my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you'll never ever betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:50.70,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx141.25\fscy142.5\pos(359,435)\frz15.126}Yamamoto Nana
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking honestly for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd never be able to go out with anyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really, really like someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over something small like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Something small like that..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...died together with the guy she loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever feel sympathy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was slowly falling into place...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...piece by piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone beloved to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I first learned what that meant... during the winter when I was fifteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:05.61,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite itsudemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:11.41,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite watashi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:16.66,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite miteite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:21.83,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mama zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.13,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Te no hira no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:28.01,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,afuredashisou na
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:33.80,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ga kureta "hajimete"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:39.60,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi hitori ja kokoro ga yuretara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:45.90,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Minna koborete shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:53.70,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata no ookina te de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:59.37,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi goto tsukamaeteite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:05.25,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Konna ni mo konna ni mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:11.43,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tayorinai watashi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:17.85,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dakedo ima wa anata no te wa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:20.64,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,sukoshi tookute
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:41.08,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite yasashiku
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:46.79,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite anata no
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.79,0:24:52.55,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite sono te de
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.55,0:24:55.47,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsundeite ne
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:25:03.39,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsumo hitori de aruiteru michi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.39,0:25:07.48,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirosugite samishii dake
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.19,0:25:14.95,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari de arukeba shiawasena kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.95,0:25:21.58,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sore dake de ippai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:29.13,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ga egao dattara
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.13,0:25:34.80,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi mo onaji de itai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:05.61,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:11.41,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... look...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:16.66,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:21.83,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The "first time" you gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:28.01,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,seems like it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:33.80,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,to overflow in the palm of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:39.60,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If my heart wavered alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:45.90,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like everyone would vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:53.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:59.37,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,took hold of me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:05.25,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,even though, even though
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:11.43,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:17.85,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still stretched out your
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:20.64,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,arm and hand to me, just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:41.04,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.04,0:24:46.79,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... gentle hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.79,0:24:52.55,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.55,0:24:55.47,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and embrace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:25:03.39,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The path I always walk alone
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.39,0:25:07.48,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,is too wide, and only makes me lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.19,0:25:14.95,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,If we walked together, I'd be filled
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.95,0:25:21.58,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,with happiness, and that'd be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:29.13,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.13,0:25:34.80,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be smiling too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.90,0:25:34.93,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\pos(450,377)\fscx93.75\fscy122.5}Episode 6 Preview ...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.06,0:25:07.82,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano embraces me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.32,0:25:13.20,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's hands touch my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.20,0:25:17.20,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Yano's hands on my chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.49,0:25:19.24,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.24,0:25:20.20,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't let me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:21.41,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously not!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.62,0:25:25.54,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,She threw you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.54,0:25:28.59,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,You sisters, both older\N and younger, are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.59,0:25:32.34,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... group me with her...
